    "en": {
      "title": "CIT detained and interrogated",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Criminal Investigation Department (CIT) has taken over the investigation of the three including Vasantha Mudalike and they have been detained under 72-hour detention orders, according to Police Media Spokesperson Nihal Talduwa.",
        "He also mentioned that the Inspector General of Police has instructed the Criminal Investigation Department to investigate the conspiracy against the government.",
        "It is to be noted that Vasantha Mudalike, Hasantha Jeevanta Gunathilak and Kalveva Sirithamma Thera have been arrested under the Prevention of Terrorism Act."
      ],
